{"tid":1531552,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍 新北江 冰山一角 良心老闆","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T12:12:31.000Z","uid":300887,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ee12bc2351229b9d6b3fadee18b09a2e7cfa1344","tid":1531552,"uid":300887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNq4q9x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNq4q9x.png&h=e8818ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o3HVxPD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo3HVxPD.png&h=d4a6989c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天水圍 新天地廣場 冰山一角 良心老闆<br />\n不停同小朋友講香港人加油 又6蚊兩大球雪糕<br />\n苦中一點甜 屯門天水圍元朗既朋友認住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我以後冬天都會黎食雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可以廿蚊唔洗找或者買多杯飲品<br />\n支持一下良心小店<br />\n願老闆一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538b369d49abbcb51eeba9a5fc882944d06f311d","tid":1531552,"uid":157907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:41:56.000Z","msg":"會多d幫襯"},{"pid":"60f8b5b8b15457d8d93e732561a2e1fa27af886d","tid":1531552,"uid":37912,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:48:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71e942e53094afcb2d9db9231779bb339394d546","tid":1531552,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:17:10.000Z","msg":"感動"},{"pid":"7c175a042959a0c29bd36af218d6951915e2df3a","tid":1531552,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"由細到大呢間我真係特別鍾意佢d冷麵 個汁溝得好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6cf33e781216da13910f2bdbe77a11c78f9df0","tid":1531552,"uid":83936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"同悅湖嗰間唔知有冇關係？"},{"pid